CALIE VS the DARK REFLECTIONS OF ALICE!
This is it. The battle that you've all been waiting for and things are not looking good for our hero. Five shattered reflections of Alice take on Calie Liddle and only one will be left standing. The countdown to the special anniversary issue of Wonderland #25 continues.
